snippet.title: WWE 2K22 Top-10 Hit List of Features and Innovations
snippet.description:
Check out our unveiling of the WWE 2K22 Hit List! Take a deeper look at our top 10 features and innovations coming in March 2022! From redesigned gameplay engine, new controls, MyGM mode, and franchise-first MyFACTION are just a few to name among many more advancements headlining the most impressive WWE 2K experience to date!

WWE 2K22. It Hits 👊 Different 💥Coming MARCH 2022!

More details coming January 2022.
